    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Praetorian Specialist:</strong> 3rd level</em></p>\n<p>Your intensity in battle can shield you and help you strike true. As a bonus action on your turn, you can give yourself advantage on all weapon attack rolls until the end of the current turn. When you do so, you also gain 5 temporary hit points. The number of hit points increases when you reach certain levels in this class, increasing to 10 at 10th level and 15 at 15th level.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature three times. You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
